    "en": {
      "title": "3 people arrested with stolen goods at the Presidential Palace",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police said they have arrested 3 suspects with antiques stolen from the Presidential Palace.",
        "The President's House was seized by the protesters on July 9 following the popular uprising.",
        "In this case, only three people who stole 40 ball-shaped orbs made of brass from the windows of the President's House have been arrested.",
        "The trio were arrested yesterday while trying to sell the stolen 40 brass balls to a second-hand dealer and the items were seized."
      ],
